<p>
    Romanian Journal of Ecology & Environmental Chemistry (RJEEC) is a high quality 
    peer-reviewed scientific journal, published under CC BY 4.0 license.
</p>
<p>
    RJEEC publishes Original Scientific Studies, Review Articles, Short Communication, 
    Meeting abstracts, Conference Proceedings, all documents in English.
</p>
<p>
    RJEEC is on <b>Open Access Journal</b>, all articles being available on <a href="www.rjeec.ro">www.rjeec.ro</a>.
</p>
<p>Article processing and submission are <b>free of charge.</b> </p>
<p>
    A fast, fair and constructive peer-review process is applied.
</p>
<p>
    The journal is edited by National Research and Development Institute for Industrial 
    Ecology ECOIND in Bucharest, Romania.
</p>
<p>
    Our journal cover all topics of chemistry, ecology, environment, biotechnology, technology and cross-related 
    problems concerning research applied to environmental sciences.
</p>

